---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pricing Transparency | Healthy Paws Animal Hospital"
  description="Transparent pricing for vaccines and lab work at Healthy Paws Animal Hospital in Lake in the Hills, IL. View canine and feline wellness pricing."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-hpah-green-light py-16">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-4">Pricing Transparency</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Thank you for your interest in Healthy Paws Animal Hospital and the services we provide. As a practice <em><strong>we focus on being personal, professional, and educational</strong></em>. Transparency in what we do and how we do it allows us to provide medical options to clients that are individualized to their pet's and family's needs.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Below we have listed pricing for vaccines and laboratory work commonly discussed during our comprehensive wellness exams. Medical care for your pet is never one-size-fits-all. <em><strong>Every pet is unique, and so is every treatment plan</strong></em>. We carefully consider options, benefits, risks, and details, then work with you to create a plan tailored specifically to your pet's needs. At every visit we spend one-on-one time discussing your pet's medical, behavioral, environmental, and social history allowing us to make individualized recommendations.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/pricing-transparency-canine/" class="btn-primary">Canine Pricing</a>
        <a href="/pricing-transparency-feline/" class="btn-primary">Feline Pricing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
